Recommended IAM Policy for Infrastructure Management
==========================================================
As a Senior DevOps Engineer, you need permissions to manage the cluster's lifecycle. Avoid AdministratorAccess. Instead, use a scoped policy.

 "EKSManagement",
               "eks:DescribeCluster",
                "eks:ListClusters",
                "eks:DescribeNodegroup",
                "eks:ListNodegroups",
                "eks:UpdateClusterVersion",
                "eks:AccessKubernetesApi"
				
 "SupportActions"
                "ec2:DescribeInstances",
                "ec2:DescribeSubnets",
                "ec2:DescribeSecurityGroups",
                "iam:ListRoles"   

